'''Etymology'''
 - African

'''Meaning'''
 - Spring
   Girls named thus are meant to symbolize the beginning of life and 
   hope and the advent of happiness after a dark winter.Whether it be
   a smile that is like a flower blossoming, or it be eyes that look 
   like rose petals, Rabia's beauty is such that it pushes the observer
    to the limit of happiness and over.
   
   Rabia is also associated with divinity and pure love: [[http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rabia]Rabia of Basrah]